arm_group.description:
treatment Arm 2 will enroll and treat patients with BPM31510 at the evaluated and confirmed safe dose in combination with one of 3 chemotherapies::
Gemcitabine IV once weekly at a starting dose of 600 mg/m2;
5-Fluorouracil (5-FU) IV once weekly at a starting dose of 350 mg/m2 with leucovorin (LV) 100 mg/m2 ;
Docetaxel IV once weekly at a starting dose of 20 mg/m2
